The paper deals with image classification using various feature sources, including deep learning approaches. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the use of deep learning models and transfer learning could also place the paper under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves image datasets and their analysis, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia).
